title: Phajol Moolsan
text:
Phajol Moolsan (; ; born September 13, 1968) is a Thai <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. At the <a href="1988%20Summer%20Olympics">1988 Summer Olympics</a> he won a bronze medal in the men's Bantamweight category, together with <a href="Jorge%20Julio%20Rocha">Jorge Julio Rocha</a> of Colombia.
In <a href="Muay%20thai">Muay thai</a> his name is Put Keitlansang. ()
